{
  "stem": "8703.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But later on, I found out that this man was the leader, one of the leaders of the Polish underground.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When the guy came in, the Jew, and he squealed that we are doing, we are supplying instead 15 boxes per, per press, and we are giving-- we are producing only 14, so the Polish man had to-- to-- to explain to the-- to the [NON-ENGLISH].-- old man was that time the boss, the other one [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he didn't understand completely what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, he said to arrest Ira Kaminsky and Professor Ringel and put them-- and we will see what we're going to do with them because this is sabotage.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyway, at that time, we were very short in people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, you know, I was considered a good worker and Professor Ringel, also a good worker.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what did he do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He took me away as the man who was responsible for the production and put me to the pickrin, to the yellow production.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Professor Ringel, who was in charge of production, also at the press.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was that time the punishment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was-- in the beginning, I was a candidate to be killed, to be shot, and Professor Ringel, the same thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And instead, they put us both of us to work in the pickrin at the press.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Thank god.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After a while-- after a while at that time, from Krakow, we received about 1,500 young people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- and the commandant, the Jewish commandant from-- Isenberg was his name-- he was very, very upset about that squealing at me and Professor Ringel.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that man, for some reason, he didn't survive too long.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After about a month, he died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So as soon-- they got new--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The squealer.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
